Once per turn, during either player's turn: You can banish 1 "Ritual Beast" card from your Graveyard; this turn, all "Ritual Beast" monsters you control gain 500 ATK and DEF. You can only Special Summon 1 "Apelion the Spiritual Beast" per turn.
